Full Description: Fidg't is a centralized control point for social networks. Media handling on the mobile version includes the ability to post directly to Flickr or stream content from Last.fm. The Fidg't Visualization Tool has a wow factor to it. Windows, Mac and Linux are all supported. Fidg't's current support of social networks is limited. Three chat platforms, Flickr and Last.fm means that in its current form it's not going to appeal to everyone. Facebook, Digg, del.icio.us, Eventful and Upcoming support is planned, with the Fidg't team open to further suggestions. (Source: techcrunch.com)
